类 FeedsAdView

  • java.lang.Object
    • InterstitialView
      • cn.domob.android.ads.FeedsAdView
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    InterstitialAdListener

    public class FeedsAdView
extends InterstitialView
implements InterstitialAdListener

    A class for invoking Domob Feeds ads.

    Calls and displays Feeds ads through invoking this class.。
